  <summary date="2023-08-30T14:14:20Z" status="Introduced in House">Right to Trial Act

This bill addresses the constitutional right to a jury trial, including by (1) outlining additional factors that a court shall consider when imposing a sentence, and (2) authorizing a court to impose a sentence below the mandatory minimum.</summary>
